{"word":"ζήτημα","slug":"ζήτημα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ζήτημα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>From <a href='S:ζητέω'><el>ζητέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>that which is sought</i>, <el>οὐ ρᾴδιον ζ.</el> <i>a thing</i> not easy <i>to find</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>an inquiry, question</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a search</i>, <el>μητρός</el> <i>after</i> her, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}